properties.headline: Air Quality Alert issued January 25 at 10:22AM EST by NWS Gray ME
properties.description:
..Air Quality Alert remains in effect until 10 PM this evening...

The New Hampshire Department of Environmental Services has issued
an air quality action day for the following counties...

Cheshire.

The New Hampshire Department of Environmental Services is
predicting unhealthy air quality for sensitive groups in Cheshire
County, especially populated valley areas, through this evening.
Children, older adults, or anyone with heart or lung disease who
are in these areas should limit prolonged exertion.
